name: The Price Tag of a Feeling

metadata.name: if all love is lost
metadata.description:
"if all love is lost 
why do I still  
feel it in the wind  
it whispers 
as it runs past my ear  
everything will be fine.

if all love is lost 
why do I still  
have that photo 
hidden in my wallet  
in case we ever meet  
and I need to prove my loyalty.

if all love is lost  
why do I still  
look for you  
every time I drink 
and end up in the arms  
of a lover I don’t want to be loved by.

if all love is lost  
why do I still  
believe that it’s out there  
just waiting for the right people  
to finally be able to say  
it is the right time."

- Satvik Sethi
